# Caddy reverse proxy for Agenttic — auto-HTTPS (opt-in, profile "caddy").
# Set ASCORE_DOMAIN to a DNS name pointing at this host and bring up the caddy
# profile; Caddy provisions a Let's Encrypt cert and terminates TLS, proxying
# to the app over the compose network. Until then this stays unused and the app
# is reachable only on 127.0.0.1 (tunnel to it).
{$ASCORE_DOMAIN} {
	encode zstd gzip
	reverse_proxy app:8700
}
